== COMBINE/HARMONY Events ==

The 'COmputational Modeling in BIology' NEtwork ([http://co.mbine.org/ COMBINE]) is an initiative to coordinate the development of the various community standards and formats for computational models, initially in Systems Biology and related fields.

{{EventInfo | title = COMBINE 2015 | page = Events/COMBINE_2015 | | date = 12&ndash;16 October 2015 | location = Salt Lake City, UT, USA | summary = SBGN will be part of the sixth [http://co.mbine.org/events/COMBINE_2015 COMBINE forum].}}

